{"tid":37384,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人試過訓醒晏教情緒好低落？","createTime":"2016-12-13T10:03:23.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T10:11:13.000Z","uid":12007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"36d254298a14749835aabb6a81b4754a825cfb5b","tid":37384,"uid":12007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:03:23.000Z","msg":"試過幾次訓醒都係大約6點呢d黃昏時候，一開眼間屋暗哂，身邊乜人都無，開著左燈坐定定發呆，果一下好似入左另一個空間咁，一個無人既空間，然後情緒好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  要過一陣先正常返，有無心理撚解釋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n平時朝早訓醒有既係新鮮感，但天黑訓醒有既係失落感？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df7b59508a923de6b7e04d95e455ef757744a6c8","tid":37384,"uid":40185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:03:58.000Z","msg":"會呀"},{"pid":"81f4bfdac5a621484c9962dc68be4726e84b5fee","tid":37384,"uid":26213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:04:00.000Z","msg":"試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"182a65110b65f72e663afc7b47e3c164b5eb710e","tid":37384,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:06:52.000Z","msg":"冇咁精神姐"},{"pid":"40484ed2fb70b0653f25770201dbc2e7cda21c5d","tid":37384,"uid":12007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:07:08.000Z","msg":"點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實好撚得人驚"},{"pid":"d565bdba268e1f3df0382522faf2247b9a14d208","tid":37384,"uid":12007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:07:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇咁精神姐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔單止無咁精神，直頭係情緒低落，好自然咁放空"},{"pid":"6f7b5f57af7aa96c971994b1f4d03559dcc84d19","tid":37384,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:09:02.000Z","msg":"光線會影響你睡眠質素，好似關褪黑色素事<br />\n<br />\n利申：9up"},{"pid":"e5493e2721f86b06f8edd8e77f08cb540590fa4b","tid":37384,"uid":8483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:09:56.000Z","msg":"因為係黃昏之時，傍晚非日非夜的時候，世界的輪廓變得模糊，可以看到非人之物的時段，所以特別低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b87bdfcc81e2f74418db9866ffe4af6cdfe95a2e","tid":37384,"uid":29892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:11:13.000Z","msg":"Same here<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}